{"tid":1540460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話撤回不是真撤回 話監警會有用其實冇用","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:48:20.000Z","uid":155493,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b3dc1c77e1141fa5915a89b5920bd122dc9c02a1","tid":1540460,"uid":155493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"1.動議撤回不是已正式撤回<br />\n因為立法會太多建制議席 雖然 佢地夠膽反口既話 香港會真暴亂 所以係好大可能 會真撤回 <br />\n但現時都存在個&quot;問號&quot; 因為要等到10月先知結果<br />\n同埋佢唔係落行政命令 所以大家都仲係要睇定D<br />\n<br />\n2.監警會加人入去冇辦法清算班狗<br />\n監警會既監察能力太弱 同埋都係自己人 所以冇意思 <br />\n冇公開既獨立調查委員會都係冇用<br />\n<br />\n3.落區聽意見<br />\n其實冇意思<br />\n<br />\n4.搵人討論社會深層問題<br />\n係要做 去解決現在既社會撕裂<br />\n<br />\n同埋呢個時間講 真係似怕人權法案 <br />\n大家文宣要努力 同外國講 冇完全解決警黑暴力問題 未真正撤回送中條例 再睇下外國咩反應"},{"pid":"dc499edf02a401642a434fcc6b74d3f26630059a","tid":1540460,"uid":155493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:33:19.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"be3c84121c13403f2b8b06c156b8ccff0f446949","tid":1540460,"uid":155493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"1cea8b4d487107467274faf19151a194e4491b03","tid":1540460,"uid":155493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"f3a85644a12ef127c08b30b5106fce12e72370a7","tid":1540460,"uid":175091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:33:41.000Z","msg":"立即做中英文宣放上fb, Twitter！我地要搶風向！"},{"pid":"6a059d87d75e8d5d7047bb7ac42b96bcfc433c10","tid":1540460,"uid":155493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:33:49.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"5e26482d40b4fd0fae114e2425eaad50f273b2ce","tid":1540460,"uid":192149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:33:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5abfc8b5358f392c133594c52d038dadebd87cae","tid":1540460,"uid":155493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid